<p><b>“The Michael J Fox Show” Sweepstakes</b><b></b></p>
<p><b>OFFICIAL RULES</b></p>
<p><b>NO PURCHASE NECESSARY TO ENTER OR WIN. A PURCHASE WILL NOT IMPROVE YOUR CHANCES OF WINNING.<strong></strong></b></p>
<p><strong>Eligibility:</strong><b> </b>The<b> “</b><b>Michael J. Fox Show” Sweepstakes </b>(the “Sweepstakes”) is open to legal residents of the 48 contiguous United States and the District of Columbia (U.S.), age 18 or older at time of entry. Void in AK, HI, U.S. Territories and Possessions, Puerto Rico, outside the U.S. and wherever else prohibited by law. Employees of The Michael J. Fox Foundation for Parkinson’s Research (the "Sponsor"), its subsidiaries, affiliates, their participating advertising and promotion agencies, and the immediate family members of, and/or those living in the same household of each, are not eligible to enter. Sweepstakes is subject to all applicable federal, state and local laws and regulations.<b><i></i></b></p>
<p><strong>Entry:</strong> Visit <a href="http://www.facebook.com/michaeljfoxfoundation">www.facebook.com/michaeljfoxfoundation</a>, click "The Michael J. Fox Show” Sweeps tab, click “Like” to become a fan of The Michael J. Fox Foundation<b> </b>Facebook page <strong>and</strong> follow all entry instructions to complete and submit the online entry form. <strong>Online entries must be received </strong><b>between Wednesday, September 25, 2013 at 12:01 PM </b><b>Eastern Time (“ET</b><b>”) and Thursday, November 14, 2013 at 11:59 PM ET, <strong>(the "Sweepstakes Entry Period").</strong></b> Online entrants are subject to all notices posted online including but not limited to the Sponsor’s Privacy Policy. <b>Limit one (1) online entry per person or email address regardless if entrant has more than one (1) email address.</b> In the event of a dispute, online entries will be deemed to have been submitted by the Authorized Account Holder of the email address submitted at the time of entry. "Authorized Account Holder" means the natural person who is assigned to an email address by an Internet access provider, online service provider, or other organization that is responsible for assigning email addresses for the domain associated with the submitted email address.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><b>Prize/Approximate Retail Value (“ARV”): </b>One (1) potential Grand Prize winner will be awarded a trip for two (2), winner and a guest, for an NBC Universal Hollywood Experience Package. The Grand Prize includes two (2) tickets to VIP Universal Hollywood: VIP Experience Tour; round-trip coach airfare for two (2) to Los Angeles from winner’s nearest major airport; and three (3) night/four (4) day hotel accommodations (single standard room, double occupancy, room and tax only) (ARV $2,100.00).<b> </b>Total ARV of Grand Prize: $2,100.00.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>First Prizes: </strong>Two (2) First Prize Winners will each receive a Prize Pack which includes two (2) $40 Fandango Gift Cards (ARV $80.00), one (1) <i>Back to the Future</i> Trilogy (on Blu-ray) (ARV $60.00), one (1) NBC-branded Canvas Tote (ARV $25.00), one (1) <i>The Michael J. Fox Show</i> (27x40) Poster (ARV $20.00), one (1) <i>The Michael J. Fox Show </i>Hat (ARV $20.00), one (1) <i>The Michael J. Fox Show</i> Mug  (ARV $10.00), one<i> </i>(1)<i> </i>Paperback,<i> Always Looking Up: The Adventures of an Incurable Optimist</i> (ARV $12.00), and one (1)<i> </i>Paperback,<i> Lucky Man</i> (ARV $10.00) <strong>(ARV: $237.00 each). TOTAL ARV of all First Prizes: $474.00 </strong><strong></strong></p>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong>The total ARV of all prizes available to be won: $2,574.00. </strong></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Random Drawings:</strong> The winners will be selected in a random drawing taking place on or about <b>Thurs</b><b>day,<strong> November 21, 2013</strong></b><strong> </strong>from among all eligible entries received, <strong>which will take place</strong> at the offices of The US Sweepstakes &amp; Fulfillment Company, an independent agent of the Sponsor whose decisions are final.</p>
<p><strong>Grand Prize winner will be notified by email and confirmed in writing, and will be required to sign and return, within ten (10) days of winner notification, an Affidavit of Eligibility, a Liability Waiver, and where allowable, a Publicity Release (collectively, "the Releases"). Prize package will be awarded within approximately Forty-five (45) days after the winner is verified.  </strong>Travel companion of winner will also be required to sign a travel liability waiver. Noncompliance will result in disqualification and an alternate winner may be selected. Trip must be taken by<b> 11/14/2014 </b>or prize will be forfeited in its entirety.<strong></strong></p>
<p><strong>First Prize winners </strong>will be notified by email and requested to confirm their mailing address within 48 hours via return email. <u>Prizes will be sent to the address on the entry form or new address provided via email within 4-6 weeks of winner being verified.</u><strong></strong></p>
